ul.li:
Copy Location - copies an application
          specific URL for the selected resource to the clipboard. You can use this URL for various
          actions like opening or transforming the resources;

Check In - checks in the selected document on the server. This
        action opens the Check In dialog. In this dialog, the following
        options are available:

Minor Version - increments the minor version of the file on the
            server;

Major Version - increments the major version of the file on the
            server;

Overwrite - overwrites the latest version of the file on the
            server;

Comment - allows you to comment on a file that you check
            in;
